title: I'm Sprung and I Can't Move On

description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, my ex-girlfriend and I had been together for many years, but we recently broke up because she was selfish and didn’t want to get married. We broke up about six months ago, but we continued to have sex because that’s the one thing that she does very well....
